sections.heading: Kerosene; use or storage; container or portable tank prohibited
sections.text: No person keeping for use or using kerosene, otherwise known as coal oil, shall put or keep the same in any container or portable tank painted or stamped as provided by section 66-103.SourceLaws 1907, c. 86, ยง 4, p. 305;R.S.1913, ยง 5757
